Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:51.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫パカパカ パカパカ…(足音)\N(ﾎｰｸ)おうっ こら～！
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.24,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! You've got a lot of nerve messing with me! You bastard pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:53.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきは\Nよくも やってくれやがったな➡
